title: Beavis and Butthead Season 3 - Uncut
description:
Since the other torrent was not moving, I decided to upload Season 3 of Beavis and Butthead from my own rips.  These are ripped from VHS to DVD, then from DVD to Xvid.  The image quality is about 7/10, but they are very watchable.

This torrent includes all 28 episodes from Season 3, and have only been edited to remove commercials.

Each episode is encoded at 640x480, 100MB per show.  Each show is approximately 10-11 minutes in length, except for double episodes such as "Kidnapped" and "Citizen Butthead", which are twice the length and encoded at 200MB each.

Enjoy!  And don't forget to seed!
